Beraninya kau menginjakkan kaki di duniaku tanpa permisi.

00:21:22.670 --> 00:21:23.820
Pak Tua!

00:21:26.020 --> 00:21:28.650
Enyahlah, lalat.

00:22:15.800 --> 00:22:17.300
Kau ingin membunuhku?

00:22:17.950 --> 00:22:19.520
Boleh juga.

00:22:24.540 --> 00:22:27.280
Kalau begitu, cepat lakukan dan antarkan aku...

00:22:27.500 --> 00:22:29.330
...menuju dunia kehampaan.

00:22:35.470 --> 00:22:36.290
Hentikan!

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:39.130
Sudah hentikanlah, Senji.

00:22:39.610 --> 00:22:40.670
Kau ini...

00:22:41.010 --> 00:22:43.850
Bukanlah orang sebiadab mereka!

00:22:45.340 --> 00:22:46.440
Pak Tua...

00:22:49.640 --> 00:22:50.800
Menyedihkan.

00:22:53.140 --> 00:22:54.010
Senji!

00:23:13.790 --> 00:23:15.610
Sssayat.

00:23:24.790 --> 00:23:26.840
Merepotkan.

00:23:38.200 --> 00:23:40.240
Ugachi sudah ditangkap?

00:23:41.180 --> 00:23:43.820
Ya, baiklah.

00:23:46.550 --> 00:23:48.440
Senji Kiyomasa...

00:23:48.760 --> 00:23:54.190
Suatu saat jika kau berhadapan denganku...

